            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the potatoes are cooking, tear your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> roughly into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>ciabatta pieces </strong>to a bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>croutons</strong></p><p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1651580971342-x200.jpg",
