    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes have had an initial 20 min, remove the baking tray from the oven and carefully cut the potatoes in half, then press down hard with a spatula to flatten them – these are your <strong>baked potatoes</strong></p><p>Fluff the insides with a fork and add a little <strong>butter</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>",
