            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the<strong> tomato base </strong>equally between the baked potatoes, then top with the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>mozzarella</strong> and <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>pepperoni</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>croutons </strong>to the other side of the baking tray and return the tray to the oven for 5-6 min or until the croutons are golden and the cheese has melted – these are your <strong>pepperoni pizza baked potatoes</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3? Use 2 trays!</p>",
      "order": 6,
