          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst everything is in the oven, chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely, then wash your<strong> lettuce </strong>and <strong>rocket</strong> and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Remove 3 leaves for per person from the <strong>lettuce</strong> and shred the <strong>inner core</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>lettuce leaves </strong>and<strong> shredded lettuce</strong> to the dressing with the<strong> rocket</strong> and<strong> </strong>the<strong> chopped chives</strong></p><p>Once ready, add the <strong>toasted croutons </strong>to the salad and toss together until everything is coated in the dressing – this is your <strong>cheat's Caesar salad</strong></p>",
