    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>pepperoni pizza baked potatoes </strong>with the <strong>cheat's Caesar salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Sprinkle the <strong>remaining oregano </strong>over the baked potatoes and top the salad with the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
